The paper deals with the task of automatic live commenting, which involves both language understanding and visual comprehension. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with large-scale data processing and retrieval-based evaluation, which could also place it in the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
